<td>
<p><strong>Nick Bontorno: Still Portraits</strong></p>
<p>Exhibit: January 18 - February 8, 2013<br /><br />Opening Reception: January 17, 7-9 p.m.&nbsp;<br /><br /> Featured artist and 2009 alumni Nick Bontorno will exhibit his recent portrait paintings and etchings. &nbsp;Bontorno approaches portraiture using a false simplicity and poetry or allegory to highlight the individuality, humanity, and spiritual presence of his sitters. &nbsp;Bontorno received his MFA from BYU, Nick has done commission works and has exhibited throughout western U.S and New York, where he is from.</p>
</td>
<td style="text-align: center;"><img height="191" src="Images/spori-art-gallery/Bontorno_22x28%20(SMALL%20FILE%20SIZE).jpg" width="150" /></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>
<p><strong>Sufism: The Art of Love</strong></p>
<p>Exhibit: February 15 - March 7, 2013<br /><br />Opening Reception: February 14, 7-9 p.m. &nbsp;<br /><br />Photographer and artist Hajji Seyd Salman Chishty is a renowned Islamic Sufi from Ajmer, India. Sufism emphasizes the universal religious message that God created all nature and all humanity as an act of Divine Love, and that we should in turn love each other and all creation. Their central teaching is&nbsp;"Love toward all. Malice toward none." Sufis communicate the message of love through art, song and dance.</p>
</td>
<td style="text-align: center;">
<p><img height="54" src="Images/spori-art-gallery/sufi%20art.jpg" width="150" /></p>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>
<p><strong>Student Art Show</strong></p>
<p>Exhibit: March 22-April 12, 2013</p>
<p>Opening Reception: March 21, 7:00 pm-9:00 pm</p>
<p>Jacob Spori Art Gallery will show art works of current BYU-Idaho art students, selected by the art department faculty. This exhibition is an excellent opportunity for the campus community to see art produced by students in various forms, and is an exciting occasion for students to show their work to their peers and the public.&nbsp;<br /><br /></p>
</td>
<td style="text-align: center;"><img height="200" src="Images/spori-art-gallery/2012-10-15%2013.59.32.jpg" width="150" /></td>
